{"word":"G5021 - τάσσω - tássō - tas'-so - Addict","slug":"G5021","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τάσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tássō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tas'-so"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Addict"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C3;&#x03C9; - tasso&#x0304;</b> - <i>tas'-so</i><p/>A prolonged form of a primary verb (which latter appears only in certain tenses); to <i>arrange</i> in an orderly manner, that is, <i>assign</i> or <i>dispose</i> (to a certain position or lot): - addict, appoint, determine, ordain, set."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1296\">G1296</a>, <a href=\"#/G1297\">G1297</a>, <a href=\"#/G1299\">G1299</a>, <a href=\"#/G2004\">G2004</a>, <a href=\"#/G392\">G392</a>, <a href=\"#/G4367\">G4367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5001\">G5001</a>, <a href=\"#/G506\">G506</a>, <a href=\"#/G5292\">G5292</a>, <a href=\"#/G5293\">G5293</a>, <a href=\"#/G657\">G657</a>, <a href=\"#/G812\">G812</a>, <a href=\"#/G813\">G813</a>, <a href=\"#/G814\">G814</a>"}]}